      "title": "Standard dialogue",
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Before Tower of Life",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Wow, that looks pretty heavy."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'The Guns'",
                  "text": "Umpf! Yeah, mate...argghh...this is...umpf...hard work..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "What would happen if I were to say..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "135"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "25"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "234"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "2351..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'The Guns'",
                  "text": "Stop! Stop! Humpf...I'll beat you to...urghh...a pulp!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Okay, okay! Don't cry!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'The Guns'",
                  "text": "Why, I oughta..."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "After Tower of Life",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "What do you do when you're not lifting logs above your head?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'The Guns'",
                  "text": "In my free time?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Yes."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'The Guns'",
                  "text": "All sorts. I like...hummff...a good kebab and a cold beer down...urrghh...the pub. And for those quiet evenings...hurrr..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "'The Guns'",
                  "text": "A bit of needlepoint is always welcome."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I can honestly say you're a very original guy."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
